
# game/script.rpy:19
translate simplified_chinese start_915cb944:

    # "It's only when I hear the sounds of shuffling feet and supplies being put away that I realize that the lecture's over."
    "只有当我听到拖着脚走路的声音和物资被收起来的时候，我才意识到讲座已经结束了。"

# game/script.rpy:21
translate simplified_chinese start_d48fb984:

    # "Professor Eileen's lectures are usually interesting, but today I just couldn't concentrate on it."
    "艾琳教授的讲座通常都很有趣，但今天我就是无法集中注意力。"

# game/script.rpy:23
translate simplified_chinese start_622654e3:

    # "I've had a lot of other thoughts on my mind...thoughts that culminate in a question."
    "我脑子里有很多其他的想法……这些想法最终会变成一个问题。"

# game/script.rpy:25
translate simplified_chinese start_5aee3489:

    # "It's a question that I've been meaning to ask a certain someone."
    "这是我一直想问某个人的问题。"

# game/script.rpy:30
translate simplified_chinese start_66c6d238:

    # "When we come out of the university, I spot her right away."
    "当我们走出大学校门时，我立刻发现了她。"

# game/script.rpy:35
translate simplified_chinese start_1d44d9d7:

    # "I've known Sylvie since we were kids. She's got a big heart and she's always been a good friend to me."
    "我从小就认识希尔薇。她心胸宽广，一直是我的好朋友。"

# game/script.rpy:37
translate simplified_chinese start_1c8af99f:

    # "But recently... I've felt that I want something more."
    "但最近……我觉得我想要试试别的。"

# game/script.rpy:39
translate simplified_chinese start_17a1771f:

    # "More than just talking, more than just walking home together when our classes end."
    "不仅仅是聊天，不仅仅是下课后一起走回家。"

# game/script.rpy:58
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_cf214f74:

    # s "Hi there! How was class?"
    s "嗨！课上得怎么样？"

# game/script.rpy:60
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_f5f51c33:

    # m "Good..."
    m "挺好……"

# game/script.rpy:62
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_027fd9f0:

    # "I can't bring myself to admit that it all went in one ear and out the other."
    "我不能让自己承认这一切都是左耳进右耳出。"

# game/script.rpy:64
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_1e626e6b:

    # m "Are you going home now? Wanna walk back with me?"
    m "你现在回家吗？想和我一起走吗？"

# game/script.rpy:66
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_ed1dfb9d:

    # s "Sure!"
    s "当然！"

# game/script.rpy:71
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_03faae39:

    # "After a short while, we reach the meadows just outside the neighborhood where we both live."
    "过了一小会儿，我们来到了我们共同居住的社区外面的草地上。"

# game/script.rpy:73
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_b3b54d3c:

    # "It's a scenic view I've grown used to. Autumn is especially beautiful here."
    "这是我已经习惯了的风景。这里的秋天特别美。"

# game/script.rpy:75
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_8f173bb5:

    # "When we were children, we played in these meadows a lot, so they're full of memories."
    "当我们还是孩子的时候，我们经常在这草地上玩耍，所以这里充满了回忆。"

# game/script.rpy:77
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_aa84c954:

    # m "Hey... Umm..."
    m "嘿……嗯……"

# game/script.rpy:82
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_79becbf8:

    # "She turns to me and smiles. She looks so welcoming that I feel my nervousness melt away."
    "她转向我微笑。她看起来很热情，我觉得我的紧张消失了。"

# game/script.rpy:84
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_6a5d032c:

    # "I'll ask her...!"
    "我会问她……！"

# game/script.rpy:86
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_29e68260:

    # m "Ummm... Will you..."
    m "嗯……你愿意……"

# game/script.rpy:88
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_6c267868:

    # m "Will you be my artist for a visual novel?"
    m "你愿意成为我视觉小说的画师吗？"

# game/script.rpy:92
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_16b8cb94:

    # "Silence."
    "沉默。"

# game/script.rpy:94
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_289664f3:

    # "She looks so shocked that I begin to fear the worst. But then..."
    "她看起来很震惊，我开始担心最坏的情况。但是……"

# game/script.rpy:98
translate simplified_chinese rightaway_8cb5deeb:

    # s "Sure, but what's a \"visual novel?\"" nointeract
    s "当然，但什么是“视觉小说”呢？" nointeract

# game/script.rpy:111
translate simplified_chinese game_65cca574:

    # m "It's a kind of videogame you can play on your computer or a console."
    m "这是一种可以在电脑或主机平台上玩的电子游戏。"

# game/script.rpy:113
translate simplified_chinese game_da120cd2:

    # m "Visual novels tell a story with pictures and music."
    m "视觉小说用图片和音乐讲述一个故事。"

# game/script.rpy:115
translate simplified_chinese game_0157c4d2:

    # m "Sometimes, you also get to make choices that affect the outcome of the story."
    m "有时，你也会做出影响故事结局的选择。"

# game/script.rpy:117
translate simplified_chinese game_68b33461:

    # s "So it's like those choose-your-adventure books?"
    s "就像那些“选择你的冒险”的书一样？"

# game/script.rpy:119
translate simplified_chinese game_fa834128:

    # m "Exactly! I've got lots of different ideas that I think would work."
    m "就是这样！我有很多不同的想法，我认为是可行的。"

# game/script.rpy:121
translate simplified_chinese game_d9b28ade:

    # m "And I thought maybe you could help me...since I know how you like to draw."
    m "我想也许你能帮我……因为我知道你喜欢画画。"

# game/script.rpy:123
translate simplified_chinese game_eaa56bc9:

    # m "It'd be hard for me to make a visual novel alone."
    m "我很难独自完成一部视觉小说。"

# game/script.rpy:127
translate simplified_chinese game_9befd1bf:

    # s "Well, sure! I can try. I just hope I don't disappoint you."
    s "嗯，当然！我可以试试。我只希望我不会让你失望。"

# game/script.rpy:129
translate simplified_chinese game_c788ae90:

    # m "You know you could never disappoint me, Sylvie."
    m "你知道你永远不会让我失望的，希尔薇。"

# game/script.rpy:138
translate simplified_chinese book_4221b3bd:

    # m "It's like an interactive book that you can read on a computer or a console."
    m "它就像一本可以互动的书，你可以在电脑或主机平台上阅读。"

# game/script.rpy:142
translate simplified_chinese book_4cfd8044:

    # s "Interactive?"
    s "互动？"

# game/script.rpy:144
translate simplified_chinese book_b9c732c8:

    # m "You can make choices that lead to different events and endings in the story."
    m "你可以选择不同的故事情节和结局。"

# game/script.rpy:146
translate simplified_chinese book_1c7ac61a:

    # s "So where does the \"visual\" part come in?"
    s "那么“视觉”部分从何而来呢？"

# game/script.rpy:148
translate simplified_chinese book_763f25a8:

    # m "Visual novels have pictures and even music, sound effects, and sometimes voice acting to go along with the text."
    m "视觉小说有图片，甚至有音乐、音效，有时还有配音来配合文字。"

# game/script.rpy:152
translate simplified_chinese book_2277f2aa:

    # s "I see! That certainly sounds like fun. I actually used to make webcomics way back when, so I've got lots of story ideas."
    s "我明白了！听起来很有趣。实际上，我很早以前就开始制作网络漫画了，所以我有很多故事构思。"

# game/script.rpy:154
translate simplified_chinese book_ccd3e9b0:

    # m "That's great! So...would you be interested in working with me as an artist?"
    m "那太好了！那么……你有兴趣当画师来和我一起做游戏吗？"

# game/script.rpy:156
translate simplified_chinese book_e325967b:

    # s "I'd love to!"
    s "我很乐意！"

# game/script.rpy:165
translate simplified_chinese marry_4509e340:

    # "And so, we become a visual novel creating duo."
    "于是，我们变成了一个视觉小说创作二人组。"

# game/script.rpy:170
translate simplified_chinese marry_0f82ff7f:

    # "Over the years, we make lots of games and have a lot of fun making them."
    "多年来，我们制作了很多游戏，并从中获得了很多乐趣。"

# game/script.rpy:174
translate simplified_chinese marry_08e24a18:

    # "Our first game is based on one of Sylvie's ideas, but afterwards I get to come up with stories of my own, too."
    "我们的第一个游戏是基于希尔薇的一个想法，但之后我也会创作出我自己的故事。"

# game/script.rpy:176
translate simplified_chinese marry_285256a1:

    # "We take turns coming up with stories and characters and support each other to make some great games!"
    "我们轮流创作故事和角色，互相支持，做出一些很棒的游戏！"

# game/script.rpy:178
translate simplified_chinese marry_27260f18:

    # "And one day..."
    "终于有一天……"

# game/script.rpy:183
translate simplified_chinese marry_bf690666:

    # s "Hey..."
    s "那个……"

# game/script.rpy:185
translate simplified_chinese marry_7a5c1899:

    # m "Yes?"
    m "啊？"

# game/script.rpy:189
translate simplified_chinese marry_3c154e68:

    # s "Will you marry me?"
    s "你愿意娶我吗？"

# game/script.rpy:191
translate simplified_chinese marry_8bcbc4b9:

    # m "What? Where did this come from?"
    m "什么？这想法从哪里来的？"

# game/script.rpy:195
translate simplified_chinese marry_f913278c:

    # s "Come on, how long have we been dating?"
    s "拜托，我们约会多久了？"

# game/script.rpy:197
translate simplified_chinese marry_4ba892a0:

    # m "A while..."
    m "有一段时间了……"

# game/script.rpy:201
translate simplified_chinese marry_39d7f0df:

    # s "These last few years we've been making visual novels together, spending time together, helping each other..."
    s "在过去的几年里，我们一直在一起创作视觉小说，一起消磨时间，互相帮助……"

# game/script.rpy:203
translate simplified_chinese marry_1516df50:

    # s "I've gotten to know you and care about you better than anyone else. And I think the same goes for you, right?"
    s "我比任何人都了解你，关心你。我想你也一样，对吧？"

# game/script.rpy:205
translate simplified_chinese marry_3234b0ab:

    # m "Sylvie..."
    m "希尔薇……"

# game/script.rpy:209
translate simplified_chinese marry_8179b35b:

    # s "But I know you're the indecisive type. If I held back, who knows when you'd propose?"
    s "但我知道你是优柔寡断的类型。如果我踌躇不前，谁知道你什么时候会求婚？"

# game/script.rpy:213
translate simplified_chinese marry_373937d9:

    # s "So will you marry me?"
    s "那你愿意娶我吗？"

# game/script.rpy:215
translate simplified_chinese marry_857958dc:

    # m "Of course I will! I've actually been meaning to propose, honest!"
    m "我当然会！我其实一直想求婚的，真的！"

# game/script.rpy:217
translate simplified_chinese marry_81ed468b:

    # s "I know, I know."
    s "我知道，我知道。"

# game/script.rpy:219
translate simplified_chinese marry_1c4ae954:

    # m "I guess... I was too worried about timing. I wanted to ask the right question at the right time."
    m "我想……我太担心时机了。我想在合适的时候提这个。"

# game/script.rpy:223
translate simplified_chinese marry_0db38565:

    # s "You worry too much. If only this were a visual novel and I could pick an option to give you more courage!"
    s "你担心的太多了。如果这是一部视觉小说，我可以选一个能给你更多勇气的选项！"

# game/script.rpy:228
translate simplified_chinese marry_ca27786f:

    # "We get married shortly after that."
    "不久之后我们就结婚了。"

# game/script.rpy:230
translate simplified_chinese marry_621ed4fc:

    # "Our visual novel duo lives on even after we're married...and I try my best to be more decisive."
    "我们的视觉小说二人组甚至在我们结婚后还活着……我尽最大努力让自己更果断。"

# game/script.rpy:232
translate simplified_chinese marry_3c7f0bf0:

    # "Together, we live happily ever after even now."
    "总之，我们也会幸福地生活在一起。"

# game/script.rpy:234
translate simplified_chinese marry_2ad49007:

    # "{b}Good Ending{/b}."
    "{b}好结局{/b}。"

# game/script.rpy:240
translate simplified_chinese later_3c679c17:

    # "I can't get up the nerve to ask right now. With a gulp, I decide to ask her later."
    "我现在无法鼓起勇气去问。犹豫了一会后，我决定过段时间再问她。"

# game/script.rpy:245
translate simplified_chinese later_a77741b6:

    # "But I'm an indecisive person."
    "但我是个优柔寡断的人。"

# game/script.rpy:247
translate simplified_chinese later_982e14b6:

    # "I couldn't ask her that day and I end up never being able to ask her."
    "我那天没能问她，我最后还是没能去问她。"

# game/script.rpy:249
translate simplified_chinese later_f0f9a061:

    # "I guess I'll never know the answer to my question now..."
    "我想我永远也不会知道问题的答案了……"

# game/script.rpy:251
translate simplified_chinese later_f5219ac2:

    # "{b}Bad Ending{/b}."
    "{b}坏结局{/b}。"

